# text: In how -- in the creation of `` Lost , '' Damon Lindelof and I , who created the show with me , we were basically tasked with creating this series that we had very little time to do . We had 11 and a half weeks to write it , cast it , crew it , shoot it , cut it , post it , turn in a two-hour pilot .
